		   Xtwitter - twitter client for X

Xtwitter is very tiny twitter client for X Window System.
It'll works on Linux, and other UNIX-like operating systems.

* Project URL
  http://www.cuspy.org/xtwitter/

* Requirements

  X.org
  Imlib
  libcurl
  libxml 2.0
  glib 2.0
  libnotify(optional)

* Build

  % ./configure

  # If you want to use libnotify.
  % ./configure --enable-libnotify

  % make

* Configration

  % mkdir ~/.xtwitter
  % cat > ~/.xtwitter/config
  user=test
  pass=xxxxxxxx
  ^D

